<h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
<h2>How do I register?</h2>
<p>Registration is easy! Simply login with Facebook and we'll do the rest! Once you've logged in, you'll be promted to choose the school you attend and then you'll see your Account Home screen.</p>
<h2>How do I create my schedule?</h2>
<p>On your account home page, simply click 'New Schedule' and you'll be taken to the schedule create page where you can enter in all the classes you're taking. You can also enter in the start and end times, what days of the week the class is on and the name of your professor. This information will help show you who your classmates are!</p>
<h2>How do I see who else is in the same classes as me?</h2>
<p>Once you've added all your classes to your schedule, you can see who your classmates are by browsing to your classlist and clicking 'View Classmates'. This will show you a list of any of your Facebook friends who are in the same class section!</p>
<h2>What is the 'Wishlist' feature?</h2>
<p>There are often classes that you'd like to get into that are currently full or waitlisted. It would still be nice to see if any of your friends are going to be taking those classes next semester, right? Well you can add a class to your wishlist and check out who your potential classmates would be without it showing up on your schedule. Then, if you get accepted into the class, you can transfer it across to your schedule with the click of a button so others can see!</p>